OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,FA grandmother-of-seven says she is
OL,7,F"devastated" after being given an
OL,8,Fofficial council warning ordering her
OL,9,Fto stop feeding stray cats.
OL,11,FColette Boler, 62, has been tending to
OL,12,Fa colony of strays on an industrial
OL,13,Festate in Thurnscoe near Barnsley for
OL,14,Fthe last two decades.
OL,16,FBut following complaints from a local
OL,17,Fbusiness she has now been sent a
OL,18,Fletter by Barnsley Council, warning
OL,19,Fher to stop.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
