PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,FThe council said the cats were "having
OL,7,Fa detrimental effect, of a persistent
OL,8,For continuing nature, on the quality
OL,9,Fof life of those in the locality".
OL,11,FIf Mrs Boler ignores the ban she could
OL,12,Fface a community protection notice,
OL,13,Fwhich in turn could result in a fine
OL,14,Fof up to #2,500.
OL,16,FMrs Boler, who is affectionately known
OL,17,Fas the "crazy cat lady", said: "I
OL,18,Ftreat them as if they're my own cats.
OL,19,FI just feel so sorry that they're
OL,20,Fferal, they're out in the freezing
OL,21,Fcold."
OL,26,@yD@`OU}D@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
