OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,F"I come every single day to feed them
OL,7,Ftwice a day, even on Christmas and
OL,8,Fboxing day.
OL,10,F"Its absolutely devastating that it's
OL,11,Fcome to this."
OL,13,FMrs Boler, a former cafe owner,
OL,14,Fstarted feeding the cats while
OL,15,Fdelivering sandwiches to local
OL,16,Fbusinesses.
OL,18,FShe said she has spent thousands of
OL,19,Fpounds looking after them and has
OL,20,Fworked with rescue groups to have them
OL,21,Fneutered and treated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
