CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,FHer granddaughter said: "It's not
OL,7,Fhurting anyone. She helps flea them
OL,8,Fand capture what she can.
OL,10,F"She does what she can, she tries
OL,11,Fkeeping them fed and clean."
OL,13,FThe company behind the complaint,
OL,14,Fwhich asked not to be identified, said
OL,15,Fit had a "duty of care to provide a
OL,16,Fsafe and hygienic working environment"
OL,17,Ffor its staff.
OL,26,@nD@YOUrD@AOUsD@\O]
