PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,FIn a statement it added: "Over a long
OL,7,Fperiod of time our staff have
OL,8,Fexperienced ongoing issues with cats
OL,9,Ffouling in working areas and in
OL,10,Fmaterials used during production
OL,11,Facross our open yard.
OL,13,F"Staff have regularly had to clear
OL,14,Fanimal waste before starting work,
OL,15,Fwhich has raised understandable
OL,16,Fhygiene concerns within a
OL,17,Fmanufacturing environment."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
