PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,FBarnsley Council said it realised the
OL,7,Fsituation was "upsetting" and
OL,8,Frecognised Mrs Boler's "good
OL,9,Fintentions".
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "After reviewing
OL,12,Fevidence and previous requests to stop
OL,13,Ffeeding in this location, the council
OL,14,Fissued a community protection warning.
OL,15,FThis is not a fine or enforcement
OL,16,Faction, but an early step to prevent
OL,17,Fthe situation from getting worse.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
