OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1773346282
OL,3,C'Devastating': Grandma banned by
OL,4,Ccouncil from feeding stray cats
OL,6,F"The warning simply asks that feeding
OL,7,Fdoes not take place on public highways
OL,8,For around the industrial estate, to
OL,9,Fprotect local businesses, people
OL,10,Fworking in the area, and the animals
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"We always aim to protect public
OL,14,Fhealth and safety, and we encourage
OL,15,Fanyone concerned about stray animals
OL,16,Fto work with recognised animal welfare
OL,17,Forganisations, so support can be
OL,18,Fprovided safely."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@QO]
